&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Join the Team!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Is technology your passion? Do you want to work with smart, forward-thinking individuals? Do you want to grow in a career you love?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Align, our professionals are the key to our success. We don’t just hire talent, we invest in exceptional people who are forward-thinking, results-driven, and passionate about what they do. We’re a group of tech-savvy professionals who are motivated by making an impact. Our culture is one of unbounded opportunity that celebrates the passions, skills and ideas of our team—work hard, play hard, be smart!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We believe great communities lead to great companies. That’s why we offer a dynamic workplace where you feel inspired, engaged and innovative. We offer professionals opportunities to train in the leading technologies, make an impact within the industry and acquire valuable new skills whether on client sites or in one of our regional offices.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We are seeking a hands-on BIM Revit Manager to lead MEP modeling, BIM coordination, and team development across complex data center construction projects. This role will&amp;nbsp;be responsible for&amp;nbsp;producing and managing detailed Revit models for mechanical, electrical, plumbing, driving clash detection and coordination efforts, and mentoring a team of BIM professionals.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;This is a hands-on Revit production role focused on&amp;nbsp;mentoring and leading a team,&amp;nbsp;building&amp;nbsp;and modifying coordinated models, working across disciplines,&amp;nbsp;and producing construction-ready documentation used by field teams. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Lead hands-on Revit modeling for data center white space (MEP) systems on active construction projects&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Manage BIM coordination, clash detection, constructability reviews, and model issue resolution across MEP, structural, and architectural disciplines&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Support project teams with installation-focused modeling, drawing production, and field coordination&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Develop and maintain BIM standards, QA/QC processes, templates, and coordination workflows&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Manage, mentor, and develop a team of BIM/Revit professionals&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Partner with project managers, superintendents, engineers, and clients to ensure BIM models support successful field execution&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;7+ years of BIM/Revit experience supporting MEP systems in construction or engineering environments&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&

