&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Conduct root cause analysis on system or process issues.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
